            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 2000,
            "LocalizeKR": "…으읏, 으으읏…",
            "LocalizeJP": "んっ、くぅっ……！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20014,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2001401,
            "DisplayOrder": 520,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7667,
            "LocalizeKR": "…쳇. 내부가\n뻑뻑해서 그런지,\n조금도 움직이질 않아.",
            "LocalizeJP": "……ちっ。\n中が詰まってるのか、\n全然抜けない。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20014,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2001401,
            "DisplayOrder": 530,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 3800,
            "LocalizeKR": "좀 더,\n미끄럽게 만들지 않으면…",
            "LocalizeJP": "もっと、\n滑りを良くしないと……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20014,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2001401,
            "DisplayOrder": 540,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8033,
            "LocalizeKR": "선생님,\n그쪽에 있는 윤활유 좀\n여기로 가져다줄래?",
            "LocalizeJP": "先生、\nそこにある潤滑油を\nこっちの方にくれるか？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20014,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2001401,
            "DisplayOrder": 550,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 5500,
            "LocalizeKR": "오, 이제야 좀 괜찮네.",
            "LocalizeJP": "おっ、これなら\nいけるんじゃ……？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20014,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2001401,
            "DisplayOrder": 560,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10833,
            "LocalizeKR": "하아아… 이렇게\n녹을 벗겨내고 있을 때가\n제일 기분 좋아…",
            "LocalizeJP": "あぁ……\nこうして錆をはがしてる瞬間は、\n本当に気持ち良い……",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20014,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2001401,
            "DisplayOrder": 570,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 5300,
            "LocalizeKR": "…뭔가 손동작이 신경 쓰여서,\n똑바로 쳐다볼 수 없다고?",
            "LocalizeJP": "……何だか手つきが気になって、\nちょっと直視できない？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_05_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20014,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2001401,
            "DisplayOrder": 580,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10200,
            "LocalizeKR": "하, 하아아?! 이건 신성한\n포구 수입 작업이라고! 무슨\n헛소리야, 이 바보가!",
            "LocalizeJP": "っ、はぁぁっ！？\nこれは神聖な手入れの作業だぞ！\n何言ってんだバカ！？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
